sentences: He joined Montreal's Arcade Fire on their Neon Bible world tour in 2007–2008, playing trumpet, flugelhorn, euphonium, french horn, and flute.
He is currently arranger and conductor for Father John Misty.
Pratt is the singer and chief songwriter of Bright Moments, a Brooklyn-based indie rock band.
Their debut album Natives was released February 21, 2012 on Luaka Bop.
